{"tid":2517953,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個社會好需要學歷 講唔洗學歷注定做窮人","createTime":"2021-05-05T16:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T18:01:30.000Z","uid":146917,"like":46,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"69014991aee91834d6026721f5f4db8bfc49bfb0","tid":2517953,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:19:38.000Z","msg":"基本上 所有上市公司員工／中上產都有大學學歷<br />\n話讀書冇用 識人好過識寫根本係呃鳩你<br />\n入場卷都冇 識幾多人都冇用<br />\n因為完全唔同程度<br />\n比你識到 升職都唔關你事<br />\n做到一半發現你廢 踢走你都得<br />\n如果讀書冇用 外國都基本上唔會要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加大 英國 澳洲 美國都唔會請你<br />\n讀緊書嘅你 快撚d讀好佢再走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔走 唔想大個窮就努力讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1507da58274f7aee9e3a2a550a8b1c46c8ab0199","tid":2517953,"uid":38904,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"得啲讀唔成書嘅人先會話讀書冇用<br />\n除非你係兒仔/小部份天材<br />\n不過喺連登100%都係前者"},{"pid":"135b31295ef877d133182349120145987a995c4c","tid":2517953,"uid":130177,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"點都死個學位返嚟 野雞都一定要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405b04d7b94499842599df3481f463baaf0d860b","tid":2517953,"uid":146917,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"d人話 冇學歷都可以成功<br />\n呢個係真 但成功都上晒新聞 <br />\n1000個有1個成功<br />\n人地冇學歷但有高過正常人嘅技術<br />\n你有嘅話就唔會好似依架咁廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDSE雞 你地都係考完DSE 都係收收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f21532956ff675d8d8e2e8acc67fc3b4c08626","tid":2517953,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"睇做邊行<br />\n有啲係做住野半工讀，讀番夜校open u讀番黎"},{"pid":"b56b3cb5f57d041068cea32a1daa5fd63a4bfc60","tid":2517953,"uid":146917,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"